# ⚡ EnergyX — Notebook 01
## Thermodynamics, Heat Transfer, Fluid Mechanics & Dimensionless Numbers

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:energyx,        "~> 1.0"},
  {:kino,           "~> 0.12"},
  {:kino_vega_lite, "~> 0.1"},
  {:vega_lite,      "~> 0.1"}
])
alias VegaLite, as: Vl
```

