## 3. Heat Transfer — All Three Modes

```elixir
# Conduction
cond_result = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.fourier_conduction(%{
  k: 0.04,        # mineral wool, W/(m·K)
  area_m2: 10.0,
  delta_t: 20.0,
  thickness_m: 0.10
})

# Convection (Dittus-Boelter)
re = 50_000; pr = 0.71   # turbulent air flow
db = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.dittus_boelter(%{re: re, pr: pr, heating: true})
nu = db.nusselt
# h = Nu × k / D (D=0.05m, k_air=0.026 W/m·K)
h_conv = nu * 0.026 / 0.05

# Radiation
rad = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.radiation_net(%{
  epsilon: 0.85, area_m2: 1.0, t_hot_k: 800.0, t_cold_k: 300.0
})

IO.puts("""
Heat Transfer — Three Modes
────────────────────────────────────────────
Conduction (100mm mineral wool, ΔT=20K):
  Heat flux: #{Float.round(cond_result.heat_flux_density_w_m2, 2)} W/m²

Forced convection (Re=#{re}, Pr=#{pr}, air duct D=50mm):
  Nusselt = #{Float.round(nu, 1)}
  h = #{Float.round(h_conv, 1)} W/(m²·K)

Radiation (ε=0.85, T_hot=800K, T_cold=300K):
  Net radiation = #{Float.round(rad.net_radiation_w / 1000, 2)} kW/m²
""")
```

---

## 4. Heat Exchanger — LMTD & NTU-ε

```elixir
# Counterflow heat exchanger
lmtd = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.lmtd(%{delta_t1: 80.0, delta_t2: 20.0})

duty = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.heat_exchanger_duty(%{
  u: 500.0, area_m2: 20.0, lmtd: lmtd.lmtd_k, f: 1.0
})

# NTU method
ntu_eff = EnergyX.Thermal.HeatTransfer.ntu_effectiveness(%{
  c_hot: 10_000.0, c_cold: 8_000.0, ntu: 3.0, flow: :counterflow
})

IO.puts("""
Heat Exchanger Analysis
────────────────────────────────────────────
LMTD (ΔT₁=80K, ΔT₂=20K counterflow):
  LMTD = #{Float.round(lmtd.lmtd_k, 2)} K

Duty (U=500 W/m²K, A=20 m²):
  Q = #{Float.round(duty.duty_kw, 1)} kW

NTU-ε (NTU=3.0, C_hot=10 kW/K, C_cold=8 kW/K):
  Effectiveness ε = #{Float.round(ntu_eff.effectiveness * 100, 2)}%
  Capacity ratio C_r = #{ntu_eff.capacity_ratio}
""")
```

